<span class="line"></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>你也可以给上面这个例子显式地加上 <code v-pre>deep</code> 选项，强制转成深层侦听器：</p>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="shiki" style="background-color: var(--shiki-color-background)"><code><span class="line"><span style="color: var(--shiki-token-function)">watch</span><span style="color: var(--shiki-color-text)">(</span></span>
